      "span_text": "In the light of no single identified factor or clearly defined disease process to treat, some clinicians have successfully used a multidisciplinary model based on the management of chronic pain.  The model of care would require forming a therapeutic relationship where the experience of symptoms by the veterans is acknowledged by the clinician."
